==============================================================================================================================
响应式导航条
使用方法：
1、保证在窄屏时需要折叠的内容必须包裹在带一个div内，并且为这个div加入collapse、navbar-collapse两个类名。最后为这个div添加一个class类名或者id名。
2、保证在窄屏时要显示的图标样式（固定写法）
这里button的data-target=".navbar-responsive-collapse"表示目标是.navbar-responsive-collapse的div，
也可以写成#nav11等，这样div的.navbar-responsive-collapse可以删除，id改成nav11即可

<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
<title>响应式导航条</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="//maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.2.0/css/bootstrap.min.css">
<script src="https://www.imooc.com/static/lib/jquery/1.9.1/jquery.js"></script>
<script src="//maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.2.0/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
<!--代码-->
<div class="navbar navbar-default">
  <div class="navbar-header">
     　<!-- .navbar-toggle样式用于toggle收缩的内容，即nav-collapse collapse样式所在元素 -->
       <button class="navbar-toggle" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target=".navbar-responsive-collapse">
         <span class="sr-only">Toggle Navigation</span>
         <span class="icon-bar"></span><span class="icon-bar"></span><span class="icon-bar"></span>
       </button>
       <!-- 确保无论是宽屏还是窄屏，navbar-brand都显示 -->
       <a href="##" class="navbar-brand">慕课网</a>
  </div>
  <!-- 屏幕宽度小于768px时，div.navbar-responsive-collapse容器里的内容都会隐藏，显示icon-bar图标，当点击icon-bar图标时，再展开。
  屏幕大于768px时，默认显示。 -->
  <div class="collapse navbar-collapse navbar-responsive-collapse">
    	<ul class="nav navbar-nav">
      		<li class="active"><a href="##">网站首页</a></li>
      		<li><a href="##">系列教程</a></li>
      		<li><a href="##">名师介绍</a></li>
      		<li><a href="##">成功案例</a></li>
      		<li><a href="##"  data-toggle="dropdown">
				关于我们
				<span class="caret"></span></a> 
			<ul class="dropdown-menu">
				 <li><a href="">asd</a></li>
				 <li><a href="">asd</a></li>
				 <li><a href="">asd</a></li>
				 <li><a href="">asd</a></li>

             		</ul>
            	</li>
	 </ul>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>

==============================================================================================================================
分页导航（带页码的分页导航）
pagination-lg表示高度较大，去掉是中等高度，pagination-sm是高度较小

<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
<title>分页导航</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="//maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.2.0/css/bootstrap.min.css">
<script src="https://www.imooc.com/static/lib/jquery/1.9.1/jquery.js"></script>
<script src="//maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.2.0/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
<!--代码-->
<ul class="pagination pagination-lg">
  <li><a href="#">&laquo;第一页</a></li>
  <li><a href="#">11</a></li>
  <li><a href="#">12</a></li>
  <li class="active"><a href="#">13</a></li>
  <li><a href="#">14</a></li>
  <li><a href="#">15</a></li>
  <li class="disabled"><a href="#">最后一页&raquo;</a></li>
</ul>
</body>
</html>

==============================================================================================================================
分页导航（翻页分页导航）
previous左浮动，next右浮动

<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
<title>分页导航（翻页分页导航）</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="//maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.2.0/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <script src="https://www.imooc.com/static/lib/jquery/1.9.1/jquery.js"></script>
<script src="//maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.2.0/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
<!--左右对齐-->
<ul class="pager">
  <li class="previous"><a href="#">&laquo;上一页</a></li>
  <li class="next"><a href="#">下一页&raquo;</a></li>
</ul>
<!--禁止状态-->
<ul class="pager">
  <li class="disabled"><span><a href="www.baidu.com">&laquo;上一页</a></span></li>
  <li><a href="#">下一页&raquo;</a></li>
</ul>
</body>
</html>

==============================================================================================================================
标签:vartical-align：super可以使标签处于右上角

<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
<title>基本导航条</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="//maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.2.0/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <script src="https://www.imooc.com/static/lib/jquery/1.9.1/jquery.js"></script>
<script src="//maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.2.0/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
<p>标签<span class="label label-danger" style="vertical-align:super;display:inline-block;">pp</span></p>
<p>标签<span class="label label-warning" style="vertical-align:super;;">pp</span></p>

<span class="label label-default">默认标签</span>
<span class="label label-primary">主要标签</span>
<span class="label label-success">成功标签</span>
<span class="label label-info">信息标签</span>
<span class="label label-warning">警告标签</span>
<span class="label label-danger">错误标签</span>
</body>
</html>

==============================================================================================================================
徽章：像标签一样，使用span标签来制作，然后为他加入badge类：

<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
<title>徽章</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="//maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.2.0/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <script src="http://libs.baidu.com/jquery/1.9.0/jquery.js"></script>
<script src="//maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.2.0/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body>

<ul class="nav nav-pills">
  <li class="active"><a href="#">Home <span class="badge">42</span></a></li>
  <li><a href="#">Profile<span class="badge"  style="vertical-align:super">0</span></a></li>
  <li><a href="#">Messages <span class="badge"></span></a></li>
</ul><hr>
<ul class="nav nav-pills nav-stacked" style="max-width: 260px;">
      <li class="active"><a href="#"><span class="badge pull-right">42</span>Home</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">Profile</a></li>
      <li><a href="#"><span class="badge pull-right">3</span>Messages</a></li>
</ul>
<br />
<!--按钮勋章-->
<button class="btn btn-primary" type="button">
      Messages <span class="badge">4</span>
</button>
</body>
</html>

==============================================================================================================================
缩略图（一）
.col-xs- 超小屏幕 手机 (<768px)
.col-sm- 小屏幕 平板 (≥768px)
.col-md- 中等屏幕 桌面显示器 (≥992px)
.col-lg- 大屏幕 大桌面显示器 (≥1200px)
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4 col-lg-3">表示：
手机一行显示1个，平板一行2个，显示器3个，宽屏4个。这个取决于屏幕宽度

<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
<title>缩略图</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="//maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.2.0/css/bootstrap.min.css">
<script src="http://libs.baidu.com/jquery/1.9.0/jquery.js"></script>
<script src="http://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.2.0/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
<h1>简单的缩略图</h1>
<div class="container">
    <div class="row">
		<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4 col-lg-3">
			<a href="#" class="thumbnail">
				<img alt="100%x180" src="http://img.mukewang.com/5434eba100014fe906000338.png" style="height: 180px; width: 100%; display: block;" >
			</a>
		</div>
	<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4 col-lg-3">
			<a href="#" class="thumbnail">
				<img alt="100%x180" src="http://img.mukewang.com/5434eba100014fe906000338.png" style="height: 180px; width: 100%; display: block;">
			</a>
		</div>
	<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4 col-lg-3">
			<a href="#" class="thumbnail">
				<img alt="100%x180" src="http://img.mukewang.com/5434eba100014fe906000338.png" style="height: 180px; width: 100%; display: block;">
			</a>
		</div>
		<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4 col-lg-3">
			<a href="#" class="thumbnail">
				<img alt="100%x180" src="http://img.mukewang.com/5434eba100014fe906000338.png" style="height: 180px; width: 100%; display: block;">
			</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>

==============================================================================================================================
缩略图（二）
thumbnail写在外层div里，可以包裹全部内容。外层div里的内容如果高度不一样，float的时候会出现bug
.caption的作用如下
.thumbnail .caption {padding: 9px;color: #333;}

<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
<title>缩略图</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="//maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.2.0/css/bootstrap.min.css">
<script src="http://libs.baidu.com/jquery/1.9.0/jquery.js"></script>
<script src="http://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.2.0/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
<h1>简单的缩略图</h1>
<div class="container">
    <div class="row">
		<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4 col-lg-3 thumbnail">
